  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2 \u0ba4\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Colombo is at a standstill today with many sides demonstrating in support of the huge protest against the impeachment of the President",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Huge protest today in Khali Mukatidal to impeach the President: Colombo at a standstill",
        "COLOMBO - Today marks the completion of 3 months since the self-insurgency started by young people in the Galle face-off protest demanding the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his government. A demonstration will be held.",
        "Today's demonstration has been organized by empty-faced demonstrators without the involvement of any political party.",
        "Kota - Today's demonstration will be carried out under the theme that we will make the Ranil government resign.",
        "In addition, major political parties including United People's Shakti, People's Liberation Front, civil society organizations and religious leaders have organized different rallies and demonstrations in support of this.",
        "In view of the widely organized demonstrations in Colombo, security measures have been strengthened since yesterday by the armed forces and the police.",
        "However, Kemunu Wijeratne, president of the All Sri Lanka Bus Owners Association, said that they will not provide any bus through their association to visit the demonstrations from other districts.",
        "In order to show support for today's demonstration, Buddhist religious leaders have engaged in a satyagraha protest at Kurakottai Arasamara Junction since Thursday 07th.",
        "They will march from there this morning and participate in the empty-face protest.",
        "A large number of young people from Negombo, including young women, will arrive in Colombo by bicycle to participate in the Empty Face Demonstration.",
        "They started their rally on 07th. They started the rally on Thursday and stayed in Negombo - Kota Ko Kama that night and started the rally to Colombo again on Friday morning.",
        "Those who were participating in the demonstration said that they had personally engaged in such activities to eradicate the slave culture in the country.",
        "In order to show their support for today's demonstration, the All University Students' Union organized a massive rally from Kelani University campus yesterday. It is noteworthy that they will participate in the demonstration to be carried out today.",
        "Meanwhile, a large number of people from districts like Kurunakal, Kota Ko Kama, Kandy, and Monarakala will come by bicycle to participate in today's demonstration. It is noteworthy that they had started their rally yesterday."
      ],
